    {
      "id": "step-10-wrap-up",
      "title": "Wrap Up — Where to Go Next",
      "description": "You've now seen the full Multica codebase: the shared headless packages, the web app, the Go backend, the real-time and agent runtime, and the database. Three things to remember: business logic is platform-agnostic, the web app's bridge is the only place that knows about Next.js, and agents are first-class actors orchestrated by the task service. Pick a feature you care about and dive in — the same patterns repeat across every domain.",
